<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>ArthAI | Manage अर्थ to create अर्थ</title>

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:Inter, Arial, sans-serif;
}

body{
    background:#07111f;
    color:white;
}

html{
    scroll-behavior:smooth;
}

nav{
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    padding:25px 8%;
    align-items:center;
    position:sticky;
    top:0;
    background:#07111fcc;
    backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
}

.logo{
    font-size:28px;
    font-weight:800;
    color:#6ee7b7;
}

button{
    background:#6ee7b7;
    border:none;
    padding:14px 25px;
    border-radius:30px;
    cursor:pointer;
    font-weight:bold;
    transition:.3s;
}

button:hover{
    transform:scale(1.08);
    box-shadow:0 0 25px #6ee7b7;
}

.hero{
    min-height:90vh;
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
    text-align:center;
    padding:50px 10%;
}

.hero h1{
    font-size:60px;
}

.hero span{
    color:#6ee7b7;
}

.hero p{
    margin:25px;
    font-size:20px;
    color:#cbd5e1;
}

.meaning{
    margin-top:20px;
    color:#94a3b8;
}


section{
    padding:80px 10%;
}


.cards{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));
    gap:25px;
}


.card{
    background:#101c32;
    padding:30px;
    border-radius:25px;
    transition:.4s;
    border:1px solid #1e293b;
}


.card:hover{
    transform:translateY(-12px);
    background:#162641;
    box-shadow:0 20px 50px #0008;
}


.card h3{
    color:#6ee7b7;
    margin-bottom:15px;
}


.chat{
    position:fixed;
    bottom:30px;
    right:30px;
    background:#101c32;
    width:300px;
    padding:20px;
    border-radius:25px;
    box-shadow:0 20px 60px black;
}


.chat input{
    width:100%;
    padding:12px;
    margin-top:15px;
    border-radius:20px;
    border:none;
}


.dashboard{
    background:#0f172a;
    border-radius:30px;
    padding:40px;
}


.progress{
    height:10px;
    background:#334155;
    border-radius:20px;
}


.fill{
    width:70%;
    height:100%;
    background:#6ee7b7;
    border-radius:20px;
}


footer{
    text-align:center;
    padding:40px;
    color:#94a3b8;
}

</style>

</head>


<body>


<nav>

<div class="logo">
ArthAI
</div>

<button>
Start Planning
</button>

</nav>



<div class="hero">

<div>

<h1>
Manage <span>अर्थ</span><br>
to create <span>अर्थ</span>
</h1>


<p>
AI-powered personal finance companion helping you manage wealth,
make smarter decisions and create meaningful financial goals.
</p>


<div class="meaning">

अर्थ = Wealth / Property → Manage your resources  
<br>
अर्थ = Meaning / Purpose → Create a meaningful life

</div>

<br>

<button>
Try ArthAI
</button>

</div>

</div>





<section>

<h2>
How ArthAI Works
</h2>

<br>


<div class="cards">


<div class="card">
<h3>1. AI Onboarding</h3>

OCR reads PAN/Aadhaar images and auto-fills details.
A conversational AI replaces boring forms.
</div>


<div class="card">
<h3>2. Income Intelligence</h3>

For freelancers and entrepreneurs,
AI estimates realistic monthly averages from irregular income.
</div>



<div class="card">
<h3>3. Risk Understanding</h3>

AI detects contradictions:
"high risk appetite" but "cannot handle losses"
and asks follow-up questions.
</div>


<div class="card">

<h3>4. Goal Intelligence</h3>

"Buy a house in Bhubaneswar"

AI estimates realistic goal ranges automatically.

</div>



<div class="card">

<h3>5. Transparent Allocation</h3>

Rules-based allocation engine creates a clear,
compliance-friendly financial roadmap.

</div>



<div class="card">

<h3>6. AI Explanation</h3>

Instead of confusing charts:

"Your portfolio balances growth and stability because..."

explained simply.

</div>


</div>

</section>






<section>


<div class="dashboard">


<h2>
Your AI Financial Dashboard
</h2>


<br>

<p>
Goal: Home Purchase
</p>


<div class="progress">
<div class="fill"></div>
</div>


<br>


<p>
AI Explanation:

"Your current allocation focuses on stability because
your emergency fund is incomplete and your goal timeline
requires controlled risk."
</p>


<br>


<button>
Ask why not more equity?
</button>


</div>



</section>






<section>


<h2>
CFP + AI Collaboration
</h2>

<br>


<div class="cards">


<div class="card">

<h3>
AI Briefing Note
</h3>

Before meeting a CFP:

"User has moderate risk profile.
Emergency fund incomplete.
Goal timeline conflicts with aggressive answers."

</div>



<div class="card">

<h3>
Compliance Shield
</h3>

AI scans explanations and CFP notes
to flag language that becomes financial advice.

</div>


</div>


</section>





<div class="chat">


<h3>
ArthAI Assistant 🤖
</h3>


<p id="reply">
Hi! Want to know how ArthAI works?
</p>


<input 
placeholder="Ask me..."
onkeypress="
if(event.key==='Enter'){
document.getElementById('reply').innerHTML=
'Upload your details, answer a few questions, and ArthAI creates your financial roadmap.';
this.value=''
}
">


</div>



<footer>

© 2026 ArthAI  
<br>
AI-powered financial clarity

</footer>



</body>
</html>